                        <p>Mr. N. Subhash has played a pivotal role in fostering the growth of the institute...Mr. N. Subhash has been instrumental in driving the growth and success of the institute through his visionary leadership and unwavering commitment to excellence. Under his guidance, the institute has not only expanded its academic offerings but also enhanced its reputation as a premier educational institution. His dedication to fostering a collaborative environment and encouraging innovation has empowered both faculty and students to achieve new heights in their respective fields, making a lasting impact on the community and the future of the institute.</p>
